      "writtenOn": "2018-09-04T18:55:16Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "That is true, and we used to support that. I\u0027ve been wondering when we took it out (or alternatively, whether my memory was deceiving me), but I\u0027ve finally tracked it down. Matt disabled it as part of a larger change to add transforms to SkJpegCodec (https://codereview.chromium.org/2174493002/). He did have a comment about why he removed it (https://codereview.chromium.org/2174493002/diff/60001/src/codec/SkJpegCodec.cpp#oldcode402): \n\n\"This was a dumb feature that nobody uses and currently isn\u0027t being tested.\"",
      "parentUuid": "0d07e9db_6633d960",
